Half-Wave Rectify / Octave-Up
  - Jimi Hendrix — "Purple Haze" (Roger Mayer Octavia — the exact circuit in your
  Octavia lab)
  - Hendrix — "Who Knows" (Band of Gypsys, Octavia into a cranked Marshall — the
  ghostly octave-up shimmer on the high notes)
  - Jack White — "Blue Orchid" (Digitech Whammy doing octave-up, same principle as
  rectification)
  - The Beastie Boys — "Sabotage" (octave fuzz tones throughout)
